25. inte - ännu (for negative sentence structure  - having no effect on real distance change): 1
26. kommit - igång : igång head below (kommit - same) - 3 (still below it stands because having effect just by choosing its correct head below and choosing right most when having two heads possible distance of -3+4 can also be counted towards including flexibility determining head.)
27. igång - (kommit or som above - not considering second possible above 'som' now ignored) -1 +3 = 2
